stateDiagram-v2

    Idle --> Connecting : WiFiEvent#colon;#colon;Connect
    Connecting --> Active : WiFiEvent#colon;#colon;Connected
    Connecting --> Failed : WiFiEvent#colon;#colon;CheckTimeout<br/>[ if ctx.timer.is_expired() ]
    Active --> Idle : WiFiEvent#colon;#colon;Disconnect
    Failed --> Connecting : WiFiEvent#colon;#colon;CheckTimeout<br/>[ if ctx.timer.is_expired() and ctx.retry_count<ctx.max_retries ]
